        {
            "title": "亞洲外匯市場觀望伊朗外交進展;印度盧比創新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kcXqOjtToEKJ7ije9qa0Gw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB3Q04T_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週五亞洲多數貨幣變動不大,美元維持堅挺,投資者謹慎評估緩和中東緊張局勢的努力及其對油價的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數在亞洲交易時段下跌0.1%,結束連續三天的漲勢。截至美國東部時間00:26(格林威治標準時間04:26),美元指數期貨也下跌0.1%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>特朗普暫停攻擊伊朗能源基礎設施</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特朗普週四表示,應德黑蘭要求,他將暫停攻擊伊朗能源基礎設施10天,並補充說與德黑蘭的談判「進展非常順利」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f6cb846b-23f0-340a-a867-cf5444e68155-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一宣布有助於穩定全球市場,此前數週因美國與以色列和伊朗的衝突導致市場波動加劇,儘管交易員仍對局勢突然逆轉保持警惕。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們的基本預期仍然是美伊衝突相對短暫,地緣政治風險溢價最終會消退。然而,風險傾向於衝突更加持久,導致能源價格在更長時間內維持高位,」三菱日聯金融集團分析師在報告中表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在亞洲外匯市場,能源進口依賴度最高的貨幣仍最容易受到中東緊張局勢進一步升級的影響,尤其是韓元和日元,」他們補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日元兌美元USD/JPY下跌0.1%,而韓元兌美元USD/KRW變動不大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣在岸匯率USD/CNY上漲0.1%,而新加坡元兌美元USD/SGD持平。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度盧比創歷史新低</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度盧比兌美元USD/INR下跌0.1%至94.174盧比,此前盤中觸及94.301盧比的歷史高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外,澳元兌美元AUD/USD上漲0.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元持續獲得支撐,因市場持續預期美國利率將在更長時間內維持高位,特別是在本月稍早油價飆升引發通脹擔憂之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中東緊張局勢最嚴峻時,原油價格曾短暫飆升至每桶120美元附近,引發對能源驅動型通脹衝擊的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在地緣政治不確定性加劇和股市避險情緒的背景下,『更長時間維持高位』的美國利率繼續支撐美元,同時令亞洲外匯處於守勢,」三菱日聯金融集團分析師補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%A7%80%E6%9C%9B%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%A7%E6%AF%94%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-053431351.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 14:00:22",
